    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives just like it rolled off the showroom floor yesterday! I have pampered this car since day one, and it\u2019s been kept tucked away safely in the garage. If you\u2019re looking for that perfect, like-new feel without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. It\u2019s a total dream to drive and I'm so excited for its next owner to enjoy it! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
